Titolo: Adventures of Dino Riki

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: Adventures of Dino Riki, known in Japan as Shin Jinrui: The New Type (新人類 THE NEW TYPE), is a video game released  in 1987 for the Family Computer in Japan and 1989 for the Nintendo Entertainment System in the North America. 
Despite being developed by Hudson Soft in Japan, it was published there by Rix Soft, making it the sole video game ever released by this company. In North America, the game was published by Hudson Soft.